snippet.title: Super Mario 64 Peach's Memory Release and Download!
snippet.description:
After almost 2 years it is finally here! Delayed a lot but better late than never. 60 stars to collect, have fun!

Download: https://drive.google.com/open?id=1eNGOsvbq7w2sKL0_BM8uAyin-DGLQVDT
How to patch BPS: https://youtu.be/dDNMz2SyGtY
How to set up the emulator (ft. 12 year old me): https://youtu.be/4BtpkZ1tkXE
Discord: https://discord.gg/ycayMA4
Song is F777 Yin and Yang, its a reference to the Green Stars release trailer which used the same song, and Peach's Memory was originally the Red Stars.
